title: Chet Faker - Built on Glass
description:
Enjoy this newly released album from Chet Faker, Australian Electronica musician. Encoded with LAME at V0, the highest quality variable bitrate setting of LAME.

HAVE A GREAT DAY! :)

Description: Chet Faker (born Nicholas James Murphy) is an Australian electronica musician. In 2012 he signed to Downtown Records in the United States and issued an extended play, Thinking in Textures. In October that year he won 'Breakthrough Artist of the Year' and Thinking in Textures won 'Best Independent Single/EP' at the Australian Independent Records Awards. In January 2013 the work won 'Best Independent Release' at the Rolling Stone Australia Awards for 2012. His debut album 'Built on Glass' is out April 2014 via Future Classic / Downtown.
